    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"3dprinter_close.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/3dprinter_close.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640499/3dprinter_close.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640511\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"3dprinter_close.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"63f354e1-da8d-4aa7-8cb3-a96131209ac2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/3dprinter_close.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/3dprinter_close.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>Solaris provides various LOP nodes to create and edit USD primitives. </p><p>On the following subset of LOP nodes in addition to the common USD parameters, you will find a “RenderMan” tab to be able to specify RenderMan specific attributes: </p><p>Camera, Light, Render Var, Render Product, Render Settings, Render Geometry Settings.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=294\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"484\" data-width=\"1250\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640520\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fa34ce5b-c160-4d47-84c0-3f368d4fa277\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1250&amp;height=484 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=294 1x\"></span><p>From Houdini 20.5.486, if those “RenderMan” tabs are missing or out-of-date, SideFx provides a way to rebuild them. </p><p>You can select single or multiple nodes and click on </p><p><em>Initialize Parameters -&gt; Rebuild Renderer-Specific Parameters</em></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076526&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=295\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076526&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"487\" data-width=\"1253\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640517\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4dda57ac-0d02-40b7-a182-37954051942b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076526&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1253&amp;height=487 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076526&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=295 1x\"></span><p>It is also possible to update your whole scene by clicking the Render option from the top menu </p><p><em>Render -&gt; Rebuild All Renderer-Specific LOP parameters</em></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"336\" data-width=\"907\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640514\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640499\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1af3d7f8-8013-428d-9e9d-034bf061fb63\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=907&amp;height=336 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640499/RenderMan_Solaris_LOPS3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433076525&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=281 1x\"></span>"
